		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林从远处猛地冲来，用爪子划过平台，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林将头甩上平台，造成<span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害，停留数秒后离去。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林下潜，并从对面超远处平台冒出，蓄力施放巨大的能量球，对整个平台造成<span color="#b9b9b9">200%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="312" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">千风之护：生命盾，继承20%特瓦林生命值。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1391" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_16.png')" x="719" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_18.png')" x="719" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_19.png')" x="720" y="809">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林趴在平台上，吐出疾风，持续造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害，从一侧开始扫过平台大部分区域。技能期间有</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25%减伤</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林离开平台，一左一右地发射风弹，每次2个，每个造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害。技能期间有</span><span color="#ffdfbf">95%减伤</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林使玩家附近的3个平台开裂，造成伤害，在一次战斗中至多施放3次。<br/>设造成伤害的次数为n，则该次受到的伤害值为<span color="#7fffd7">3×n%</span><span>的伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，n值初始为1，最大为100，即</span><span color="#7fffd7">300%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#00ae83" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#00ae83">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_20.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1391" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="425" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林盘旋升空，在所有平台周期性产生5道星陨阵，每个星陨阵造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害；特瓦林倒地则暂停施放，恢复后继续；在一次战斗中本技能至多施放1次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1268" y="619" blendMode="normal">
