		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_32.png')" x="1248" y="374" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_33.png')" x="576" y="598" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/特瓦林.assets/Image_34.png')" x="576" y="822" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="864" width="432" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">减伤：在特瓦林从地下升起、「终天的闭幕」吼叫时、「袤远的奏鸣」施放时、「辰星的变奏」盘旋时、「暴风的狂想」蓄力时均具有<span color="#ffdfbf">95%减伤</span><span>；</span><span color="#ffdfbf">(仅初见特瓦林)</span><span>特瓦林倒地时带有额外</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25%减伤</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
	</Group>
